TI  - IP-Tag: Tag-Based Runtime 3PIP Hardware Trojan Detection in SoC Platforms
T2  - IEEE TRANSACTIONS ON COMPUTER-AIDED DESIGN OF INTEGRATED CIRCUITS AND SYSTEMS
KW  - Data-flow integrity
KW  - information flow tracking
KW  - RISC-V
