TI  - Yun: An Open-Source, 64-Bit RISC-V-Based Vector Processor With Multi-Precision Integer and Floating-Point Support in 65-nm CMOS
T2  - IEEE TRANSACTIONS ON CIRCUITS AND SYSTEMS II-EXPRESS BRIEFS
KW  - RISC-V
