TI  - The Simply-V Framework: An Extensible RISC-V Reconfigurable Soft-SoC for Open Research and Fast Prototyping
T2  - ACM TRANSACTIONS ON DESIGN AUTOMATION OF ELECTRONIC SYSTEMS
KW  - RISC-V
KW  - FPGA
