TI  - Day-Night architecture: Development of an ultra-low power RISC-V processor for wearable anomaly detection
T2  - JOURNAL OF SYSTEMS ARCHITECTURE
KW  - Low-power design
KW  - Embedded processor
KW  - RISC-V processor
KW  - System-on-chip
KW  - Processor architecture
