TI  - TinyVers: A Tiny Versatile System-on-Chip With State-Retentive eMRAM for ML Inference at the Extreme Edge
T2  - IEEE JOURNAL OF SOLID-STATE CIRCUITS
KW  - Extreme edge
KW  - machine learning (ML) accelerators
KW  - system-on-chip (SoC)
