TI  - Machine Learning Based Hardware Trojan Detection Using Electromagnetic Emanation
T2  - IEICE TRANSACTIONS ON FUNDAMENTALS OF ELECTRONICS COMMUNICATIONS AND COMPUTER SCIENCES
KW  - hardware Trojan
KW  - RISC-V
