TI  - MEG: A RISCV-based System Emulation Infrastructure for Near-data Processing Using FPGAs and High-bandwidth Memory
T2  - ACM TRANSACTIONS ON RECONFIGURABLE TECHNOLOGY AND SYSTEMS
KW  - Full-system emulation
