TI  - Expanding SafeSU capabilities by leveraging security frameworks for contention monitoring in complex SoCs
T2  - FUTURE GENERATION COMPUTER SYSTEMS-THE INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ESCIENCE
KW  - Safety
KW  - QoS
KW  - Network on chip
KW  - Mixed-criticality
