TI  - Reducing the Energy Consumption of sEMG-Based Gesture Recognition at the Edge Using Transformers and Dynamic Inference
T2  - SENSORS
KW  - transformers
KW  - sEMG
KW  - gesture recognition
KW  - deep learning
